1) Open and login to https://control.layershift.com
2) Click the "Account" tab
3) Click "Subscriptions"
4) Select the subscription you wish to terminate
5) Click "Request Subscription Termination" and follow the wizard
6) Your subscription will be terminated at the end of the current subscription period unless explicitly requested otherwise within the termination reason box (no refunds are provided for part-used subscription periods)
